title: PolitiFact: Testing Gwen Moore claim that 60% back federal funding for Planned Parenthood
text:
PolitiFact: Testing Gwen Moore claim that 60% back federal funding for Planned Parenthood By Tom Kertscher of the Journal Sentinel Oct. 14, 2015 5:00 a.m. 
Arguing against a bill that would halt federal funding for Planned Parenthood, U.S. Rep. Gwen Moore (D-Milwaukee) made this claim: 
"60 percent of all Americans do not want to see Planned Parenthood defunded."
